# ── Item photos (local + CDN only — do NOT commit to git) ────────────────────
# All seller-managed files live in content/.
# Upload photos to CDN with: pnpm upload-images
# Keep a personal backup of your content/ folder (external drive / cloud backup).
# content/**/*.json and content/config.ts ARE committed.
# content/contact/ (QR codes) IS committed — it's tiny.
# lib/generated/image-manifest.json IS committed.
content/items/**/*.jpg
content/items/**/*.jpeg
content/items/**/*.png
content/items/**/*.webp
content/items/**/*.gif
content/items/**/*.JPG
content/items/**/*.JPEG
content/items/**/*.PNG
content/items/**/*.WEBP
content/items/**/*.GIF

# ── Generated public asset copies (populated at build/dev time) ──────────────
public/items/
public/contact/

# ── Incremental upload cache (seller's machine only) ─────────────────────────
.image-cache/

# ── Generated build artifacts (rebuilt on every next build) ──────────────────
# image-manifest.json is intentionally NOT listed here — it IS committed.
lib/generated/search-index.json

# ── Editor / IDE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
